@NODE ShiningEye "Amiga on its way to paradise"

                                    \ /
                                  -- * --
                                    / \

             A little star, once born and often misunderstood,
                        is still shining down on us
                - on those who believe in this little star,
                knowing the strength behind its warm light,
                        feeling the endless universe
                         inside its slight corona.
              A star among others, at the dark sky at night.

                              But we believe !

                    For us, the way it shines and glows
                          is bright and wonderful,
                  and nobody else could ever understand !

                            A light among others
                          but a hidden conqueror !

                     Amiga is the sun we need to live !

                    Be his victim ! And be lucky, then !
                               I swear I am.

                                    \ /
